===Etymology===
Borrowed from {{bor|en|la|tangentem}}, the accusative of {{m|la|tangēns||touching}} (in the phrase {{m|la|[[līnea]] [[tangēns]]|t=a touching line}}), the [[Appendix:Glossary#present participle|present participle]] of the verb {{m|la|tangō||touch|pos=verb}}, from {{der|en|ine-pro|*tag-}}, {{m|ine-pro|*taǵ-||to touch}}. Cognate with {{cog|ang|þaccian||to touch lightly, pat, stroke}}. More at {{l|en|thack}}, {{l|en|thwack}}.
(thwack)

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|tăn'jənt}}, {{IPA|/ˈtæn.dʒənt/|lang=en}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

